02) Environmental Science and Pollution Research, 9, pp. 375-376; Varotsos, C., Airborne measurements of aerosol, ozone, and solar ultraviolet irradiance in the troposphere (2005) Journal of Geophysical Research-atmospheres, 110, pp. D09202. , doi:10.1029/2004JD005397; Varotsos, C., Modern computational techniques for environmental data; application to the global ozone layer (2005) Computational Science - ICCS 2005, 3516, pp. 504-510. , Part 3; Varotsos, C., Assimakopoulos, M.-N., Efstathiou, M., Technical note: Long-term memory effect in the atmospheric CO2 concentration at Mauna Loa (2007) Atmospheric Chemistry and Physics, 7, pp. 629-634; Varotsos, C., Cartalis, C., Vlamakis, A., Tzanis, C., Keramitsoglou, I., The long- term coupling between column ozone and tropopause properties (2004) Journal of Climate, 17, pp. 3843-3854; Varotsos, C., Kondratyev, K.Y., Efstathiou, M., On the seasonal variation of the surface ozone in Athens, Greece (2001) Atmospheric Environment, 35, pp. 315-320; Varotsos, C.A., Cracknell, A.P., Ozone depletion over Greece as deduced from Nimbus-7 TOMS measurements (1993) International Journal of Remote Sensing, 14, pp. 2053-2059; Varotsos, C.A., Cracknell, A.P., Three years of total ozone measurements over Athens obtained using the remote sensing technique of a Dobson spectrophotometer (1994) International Journal of Remote Sensing, 15, pp. 1519-1524; Varotsos, C.A., Efstathiou, M.N., Kondratyev, K.Y., Long-term variation in surface ozone and its precursors in Athens, Greece: A forecasting tool (2003) Environmental Science and Pollution Research, 10, pp. 19-23; Varotsos, P., Alexopoulos, K., Migration entropy for the bound fluorine motion in alkaline earth fluorides (1980) Journal of Physics and Chemistry of Solids, 41, pp. 443-446; Varotsos, P., Alexopoulos, K., Migration parameters for the bound fluorine motion in alkaline earth fluorides. II (1981) Journal of Physics and Chemistry of Solids, 42, pp. 409-410; Varotsos, P., Alexopoulos, K.,